The paper also deals with Bayesian networks and inference, which are topics in artificial intelligence and machine learning, respectively. Therefore, cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses information theory and the polynomial hierarchy, which are topics in theoretical computer science. Hence, cs.IT (Information Theory) is also a possible sub-category.
